pullsbody: @vladikoff - now that we maintain our own fork of jsxgettext, should we write some tests and merge this into our fork too?
pull_repo_desc: Extract gettext calls from JavaScript, EJS, and other template formats.
Extract gettext calls from JavaScript, EJS, and other template formats.
pull_commit_message:
fix(deps): Use pug instead of jade

The jade module was discontinued and had some `npm audit` warnings.

This replaces jade with pug and updates the jade parser based
on the updated AST format.

There was a problem with the original tests/outputs/jade.pot,
the two modified lines were actually incorrect when comparing
with the source.
